HEADWORD: Terminative
<hw>Ter"mi*na*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Tending or
serving to terminate; terminating; determining; definitive.</def>
<au>Bp. Rust.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>Ter"mi*na*tive*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> <au>Jer. Taylor.</au></wordforms>⟦br⟧
